snippet.textDisplay:
Chal Chaliye....
Its about the journey that one has to take to go beyond the limitations that world fences you with.
A well travelled man, who flew the nest a while ago, reflecting his journey which frames the main part of his memory wall.

He, with all his hardships, people who mattered come and gone and the fond memories between book pages, has made to the other end.
Yes alot of time as passed but it has made him alot stronger like the dried out flowers which keep their shape, colour and are still stronger against all the elements.

Now he shares his wisdom with the youth, surrounded with fresh vines of red flowers, but scared of embarking on the journey of her own and afraid of the challenges she might face.

He suggests dont shy away from life and lets get onboard of your own fate and go where your heart takes you.
The whole universe will then recognise and will conspire to make you, You!

Every journey has a beginning and its end is simply a handshake with another traveller...!!

Chal Chaliye.
